title: Anyone Beats the Original - Novel Updates
genre: Comedy   Drama   Fantasy   Josei   Romance   Shoujo
tags: Beautiful Female Lead   Criminals   Devoted Love Interests   Fated Lovers   Female Protagonist   Handsome Male Lead   Marriage   Reincarnated in Another World   Smart Couple   Transmigration
author: Baek Seoha   백서하
description:
I possessed “extra 1”, who married a criminal and died in a violent manner. 

I don’t think I need to get married. 

I proposed to another man, ran away from home, and did all sorts of other things… 

“So marry me, Evangeline Clauda.” 

Five years after possessing the character, only three weeks are left before entering the original story! 

In the end, I am proposed to by the criminal. 

Am I……really fated to have a doomed ending? 

The more I twist the original, the closer I get to the original?! 

Will I be able to safely protect my life and love and attain happiness?>
